    • TimeReport

      public TimeReport​(int timeReportId, int projectUserId, int signedById, java.time.LocalDateTime signedAt, int year, int week, java.time.LocalDateTime updatedAt, boolean finished)
      Constructor for the model class TimeReport.
      Parameters:
      timeReportId - Is the unique identifier for TimeReport.
      projectUserId - Is the unique identifier for ProjectUser.
      signedById - Is the unique identifier of the user that has signed the time report.
      signedAt - Is the time and date when the time report was signed.
      year - Is the year the time report was created.
      week - Is the week the time report was created.
      updatedAt - Is the time and date when the time report was most recently updated at.
      finished - Is whether the time report is ready to be signed or not. True means the time report is ready to be signed.
